Text: This is firmware version 11.110.03.00.00 of the Huawei E630 PC card. It'll raise your current 3.6Mpbs limit to 7.2Mbps. Worked for me, but it's only applicable on 100% Huawei-branded cards, not operator-branded versions.

Impossible. The card uses Qualcomm chipset MSM6280, limited to 7.2Mbps down and 384kbps up. http://www.cdmatech.com/products/msm6280_chipset_solution.jsp

There are no 14.4Mbps devices out.
